## Test

### Usability Testing Plan

*This project reached concept stage — 
formal testing is the proposed next phase.*

I would validate the prototype through 
moderated usability testing with 5–8 
policyholders recruited across:

- Age groups (digital natives vs less 
  tech-confident users)
- Claim types (vehicle damage, personal 
  injury, property)
- Device types (iOS and Android)

**Tasks I would set participants:**

1. Submit three pieces of evidence for 
   a fictional claim using only the app
2. Recover from an intentional error 
   state without handler assistance
3. Locate and interpret the confirmation 
   receipt email

**Metrics I would measure:**

- Task completion rate
- Error frequency and recovery rate  
- Time on task
- Qualitative feedback on confusion points

**Post-launch metrics (30/60/90 days):**

- Evidence upload completion rate vs baseline
- Inbound call volume related to evidence queries
- Average claim lifecycle reduction
- SLA compliance improvement rate

